snippet.title: Super Mario Toxic Tension - Reveal Trailer [CANCELLED]
snippet.description:
[Although the development of this mod has been stopped, the content created for it will be used in other projects, so check out the NSMBU modding scene ;) (i'll leave the original description here)] 

Super Mario Toxic Tension is a 1-world mod of New Super Mario Bros U that will hopefully be released this year (no guarantee).

This mod will contain a bunch of new stuff, so stay tuned for more info!

If you want to know anything about the mod, you can DM me on Discord: 
ruebli

If you want to know more about NSMBU modding in general, you can join the Evolution Discord server: https://discord.gg/aZAaXVJ  

Tweeeeter: https://twitter.com/_Rmbel
